REPLACE Procedure PROD_EDW_BASE.sp_RA_SALES_STAT ()
Begin
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,CHILDPRDCTID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,EXTERNALBAID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,ACCTDTLLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,PARENTPRDCTID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (PRDCTID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Product;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (PRDCTID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_PRODUCT_GROUP;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,PARENTPRDCTID      ,CHILDPRDCTID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (EXTERNALBAID ,ACCTDTLLCLEID) ON      PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,INTERNALBAID      ,EXTERNALBAID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (ACCNTNGPRDYR ,ACCNTNGPRDPRD) ON   PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;      
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (ACCNTNGPRDYR) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;      
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (ACCNTNGPRDPRD) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;   
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE) ON     PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_PRODUCT_GROUP;      
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (PARTITION) ON     PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;  
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE) ON   PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Business_Associate;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,MVTHDRDSTNTNLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Movement;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,MVTHDRORGNLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Movement;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,ACCTDTLDLDTLID,PARENTPRDCTID ,CHILDPRDCTID ,ACCTDTLDLDTLDLHDRID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Product;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,MVTHDRLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Movement;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Business_Locale;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,ACCTDTLDLDTLID ,PARENTPRDCTID ,ACCTDTLDLDTLDLHDRID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,ACCTDTLDLDTLID,PARENTPRDCTID ,CHILDPRDCTID ,ACCTDTLDLDTLDLHDRID ,ACCTDTLLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
COLLECT STATISTICS COLUMN (RA_SOURCE ,INTERNALBAID,EXTERNALBAID ,ACCTDTLLCLEID) ON PROD_EDW_BASE.RA_Acct_Dtl;
END;
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CREATE SET TABLE PROD_EDW_BASE.APS_ATORIONUNITFEEDS ,NO FALLBACK ,
     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO,
     BLOCKCOMPRESSION = NEVER
     (
      Ref_Prod_Location VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      UNIT_XSEQ INTEGER,
      STREAM_ID VARCHAR(32) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      SEQ INTEGER,
      X_SEQ INTEGER,
      X_UPDATED TIMESTAMP(0),
      X_BY VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      Create_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0),
      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0))
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX ( Ref_Prod_Location ,X_SEQ );
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CREATE SET TABLE PROD_EDW_BASE.APS_EVENTS ,NO FALLBACK ,
     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO,
     BLOCKCOMPRESSION = NEVER
     (
      Ref_Prod_Location VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      TYPE_ INTEGER,
      DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ID VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ID1 VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ID2 VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ID3 VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      START_ TIMESTAMP(0),
      STOP TIMESTAMP(0),
      START_DAY TIMESTAMP(0),
      STOP_DAY TIMESTAMP(0),
      VOLUME FLOAT,
      WEIGHT FLOAT,
      BATCH VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      COMMENTS VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      LABEL_ VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      PRODCODE VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      OPTIONS VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      REPORT VARCHAR(255) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      CASE_ VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      X_SEQ INTEGER,
      X_UPDATED TIMESTAMP(0),
      X_BY VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Z_SEQ INTEGER NOT NULL,
      PREP FLOAT,
      POST FLOAT,
      RATE FLOAT,
      COLOR SMALLINT,
      MOVEMENT_ID VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      APPLICATION_ID INTEGER,
      SERVICE INTEGER,
      EVENT_SEQ INTEGER,
      Create_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0),
      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0))
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX ( Ref_Prod_Location ,CASE_ ,Z_SEQ );
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,

     BLOCKCOMPRESSION = NEVER
     (

      Origin VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      OriginTank VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Destination VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      DestinationTank VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Comments VARCHAR(1000) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,

      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0))

CREATE SET TABLE PROD_EDW_BASE.APS_ZTANKS ,NO FALLBACK ,
     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO,
     BLOCKCOMPRESSION = NEVER
     (
      Ref_Prod_Location VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      ID VARCHAR(32) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      PROP VARCHAR(32) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,

      Model VARCHAR(100) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,

     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO,
     BLOCKCOMPRESSION = NEVER
     (

      PurposeCode VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ReferenceID VARCHAR(30) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ScheduleType VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ScheduleQuantity VARCHAR(25) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      NominationsScheduleStartDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD',
      NominationsScheduleEndDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD',
      NominationsScheduleIssueDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD',
      Company1Code VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Company1Name VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Company2Code VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Company2Name VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      PipelineNumber VARCHAR(10) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ProductQualifier VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ProductType VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      ProductID VARCHAR(10) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      BatchIdentification VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      UOM VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Reference1Type VARCHAR(75) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Reference1 VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Reference2Type VARCHAR(25) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Reference2 INTEGER,
      Company3Code VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Company3Name VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Company3ID VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,

      DateType VARCHAR(25) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,
      Nomination_Time VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC,

      last_update_dttm TIMESTAMP(0))

     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO
     (
      TicketNumber INTEGER TITLE 'TicketNumber' NOT NULL,
      TicketDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD' TITLE 'TicketDate' NOT NULL,
      TicketTime TIME(6) TITLE 'TicketTime' NOT NULL,
      TransactionType VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'TransactionType' NOT NULL,
      PipelineNumber VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'PipelineNumber' NOT NULL,
      RefNumber VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'RefNumber' NOT NULL,
      Carrier VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Carrier' NOT NULL,
      CarrierCode VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'CarrierCode' NOT NULL,
      Shipper VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Shipper' NOT NULL,
      ShipperCode VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'ShipperCode' NOT NULL,
      ShipToFromFlag VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'ShipToFromFlag' NOT NULL,
      ShipToFrom VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'ShipToFrom' NOT NULL,
      ShipToFromCode VARCHAR(2) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'ShipToFromCode' NOT NULL,
      DestLocFlag VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'DestLocFlag' NOT NULL,
      DestLoc VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'DestLoc' NOT NULL,
      DestLocCode VARCHAR(3) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'DestLocCode' NOT NULL,
      StartDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD' TITLE 'StartDate' NOT NULL,
      StartTime TIME(6) TITLE 'StartTime' NOT NULL,
      StopDate DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD' TITLE 'StopDate' NOT NULL,
      StopTime TIME(6) TITLE 'StopTime' NOT NULL,
      ProductNumber VARCHAR(2) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'ProductNumber' NOT NULL,
      Product VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Product' NOT NULL,
      TankNumber SMALLINT TITLE 'TankNumber' NOT NULL,
      NetVolume INTEGER TITLE 'NetVolume' NOT NULL,
      UOM VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'UOM' NOT NULL,
      GrossVolume INTEGER TITLE 'GrossVolume' NOT NULL,
      UOM2 VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'UOM2' NOT NULL,
      Gravity DECIMAL(10,2) TITLE 'Gravity' NOT NULL,
      GravityUOM VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'GravityUOM' NOT NULL,
      Temperature DECIMAL(10,2) TITLE 'Temperature' NOT NULL,
      TemperatureUOM VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'TemperatureUOM' NOT NULL,
      TemperatureFactor DECIMAL(10,4) TITLE 'TemperatureFactor' NOT NULL,
      DistributedMeterFactor DECIMAL(10,4) TITLE 'DistributedMeterFactor' NOT NULL,
      CompositeCorrectedFactor DECIMAL(10,4) TITLE 'CompositeCorrectedFactor' NOT NULL,
      Additive DECIMAL(10,4) TITLE 'Addtive' NOT NULL,
      AdditiveUOM VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'AdditiveUOM' NOT NULL,
      MeterQuality VARCHAR(7) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'MeterQuality' NOT NULL,
      Create_dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Create_dttm' NOT NULL,
      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Last_Update_Dttm' NOT NULL)
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX XPKPipelinekmraw ( TicketNumber ,CarrierCode );

UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX ( RA_Source ,AcctDtlID ,AccntngPrdYr ,AccntngPrdPrd )
PARTITION BY ( RANGE_N(AccntngPrdYr  BETWEEN 2000  AND 2100  EACH 1 ,
 NO RANGE OR UNKNOWN),CASE_N(
AccntngPrdPrd =  1 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  2 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  3 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  4 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  5 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  6 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  7 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  8 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  9 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  10 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  11 ,
AccntngPrdPrd =  12 ) );

     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,

     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO
     (
      Product_ID INTEGER TITLE 'ProductID' NOT NULL,
      Ref_Prod_Location VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Location' NOT NULL,
      Eff_Date DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD' TITLE 'Eff_Date' NOT NULL,
      Net_Quantity FLOAT TITLE 'NetQuantity',
      Terminal_ID INTEGER TITLE 'Terminal_ID',
      Create_dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Create_dttm',
      Last_update_dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Last_update_dttm',
      Master_Code VARCHAR(32) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC)
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX XPKterminal ( Product_ID ,Ref_Prod_Location ,
Eff_Date )
INDEX IDX_RefProdLocProdID ( Product_ID ,Ref_Prod_Location )
INDEX IDX_EffDate ( Eff_Date );
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CREATE SET TABLE PROD_EDW_BASE.WESTERN_PRICE_RAW ,NO FALLBACK ,
     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO
     (
      Terminal_Desc VARCHAR(30) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Terminal Desc' NOT NULL,
      Product_Desc VARCHAR(30) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Product Desc' NOT NULL,
      Channel CHAR(1) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Channel' NOT NULL,
      Event_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Event Dttm' NOT NULL,
      Rack_Price DECIMAL(12,4) TITLE 'Rack_Price',
      Prior_Date_Change_Amt DECIMAL(12,4) TITLE 'Prior_Date_Change_Amt',
      Create_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Create_Dttm',
      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Last_Update_Dttm')
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX XPKWestern_price_raw ( Terminal_Desc ,Product_Desc ,
Channel ,Event_Dttm );
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CREATE SET TABLE PROD_EDW_BASE.WESTERN_PRICE_STG ,NO FALLBACK ,
     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,
     NO AFTER JOURNAL,
     CHECKSUM = DEFAULT,
     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO
     (
      Terminal_Desc VARCHAR(30) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Terminal Desc' NOT NULL,
      Product_Desc VARCHAR(30) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Product Desc' NOT NULL,
      Channel CHAR(1) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC TITLE 'Channel' NOT NULL,
      Event_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Event Dttm' NOT NULL,
      Rack_Price DECIMAL(12,4) TITLE 'Rack_Price',
      Prior_Date_Change_Amt DECIMAL(12,4) TITLE 'Prior_Date_Change_Amt',
      Create_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Create_Dttm',
      Last_Update_Dttm TIMESTAMP(0) TITLE 'Last_Update_Dttm')
UNIQUE PRIMARY INDEX XPKWestern_price_Stg ( Terminal_Desc ,Product_Desc ,

     NO BEFORE JOURNAL,

     DEFAULT MERGEBLOCKRATIO
     (
      ord_number VARCHAR(12) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
      crude_fuel_ind CHAR(1) CHARACTER SET LATIN NOT CASESPECIFIC NOT NULL,
